Ranger Help for: adapt
======================

SYNTAX:      adapt <arctic/desert>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   6
BASE SP:     30
SKILL TYPE:  defensive

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to adapt their body to extreme climates,
reducing the environmental damage caused by harsh arctic cold or
scorching desert heat. The Ranger must specify which climate to adapt
to. The adaptation lasts for a duration that depends on the Ranger's
constitution and skill level. Only one adaptation can be active at a
time. This skill is essential for Rangers who venture into the most
extreme terrains of Darkwind.
